<para style="q1">

<verse number="9" style="v" />At the time of your anger, you will burn them up as in a fiery furnace.</para>

<para style="q1">Yahweh will consume them in his wrath,</para>

<para style="q1">and the fire will devour them.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="10" style="v" />You will destroy their offspring from the earth</para>

<para style="q1">and their descendants from among the human race.</para>
